job_history.work_description: Accepting, booking, inspecting and tracking outbound and inbound cargoes. Checking import/export documentation to determine cargo contents, and classifying goods into different fee or tariff groups, using a tariff coding system. Contacting vendors to resolve problems with shipments; Determining method of shipment, and preparing bills of lading, invoices, and other shipping documents.
